      "writtenOn": "2020-10-29T00:39:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "to me, this is better to be in the package specific to sequence number generation, rather than generic \"metrics\" package\n\nalso consider adding it in the CL where it is used.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 27,
        "startChar": 1,
