      "writtenOn": "2020-10-29T03:23:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "When I added this simple test for the search-tag metrics, I found a bug in tsmon and didn\u0027t include the metrics in this CL (find my first comment in this CL). I think such a simple test can still give us a value. \n\nI didn\u0027t add SequenceNumGenerated(). Build*() functions update more than one metric(s) conditionally and have tiny business logic. However, for metrics with a small set of metric fields, I prefer not to have an additional wrapper to update the metrics, because metric.Add()/Set() functions are simple and intuitive enough.\n\nWDYT?",
